 cc: Commissioner of Indian Affairs

Attn: Division of Tribal Government Services, Code 440
 
 

 CERTIFICATE OF RESULTS OF ELECTION

 
 Pursuant to an order of Stanley Speaks, Area Director, the attached 

Amendment IV to the Constitution and Bylaws of the Delaware Tribe of 

Western Oklahoma was submitted for ratification to the eligible voters 

of the Delaware Tribe of Western Oklahoma and was on August 15, 1981 

duly ratified by a vote of 37 for, and 4 against, in an

election duly called for that purpose.
 
 

